;Where can I buy Firefox OS?
Waar kan ek Firefox OS koop?


;To purchase a Firefox OS phone, please visit the <a href="%(link)s">devices page</a> and select your available country.
Om 'n Firefox OS-foon te koop, besoek asseblief die <a href="%(link)s">toestelbladsy</a> en kies jou beskikbare land.


;What will be the price of the phone?
Wat sal die prys van die foon wees?


;Pricing is not set by Mozilla and will be established by our operator and manufacturer partners based on local market dynamics.
Die pryse word nie deur Mozilla bepaal nie en sal deur ons operateur- en vervaardigingsvennote volgens plaaslike markdinamiek vasgestel word.


;What apps will be available on Firefox OS?
Watter programme sal op Firefox OS beskikbaar wees?


;The growing list includes leading apps like Facebook, Twitter, Nokia HERE maps, Cut the Rope, and Time Out.
Die groeiende lys sluit bekende programme soos Facebook, Twitter, Nokia HERE maps, Cut the Rope en Time Out in.


;Many more are being made available every day.
Daar word elke dag nog vele meer beskikbaar gestel.


;Is Firefox OS available in my language?
Is Firefox OS beskikbaar in my taal?


;Firefox OS is currently available in Spanish, Polish, English, Italian, Portuguese, German, Serbian, Hungarian and Greek.
Firefox OS is tans beskikbaar is Spaans, Pools, Engels, Italiaans, Portugees, Duits, Serwies, Hongaars en Grieks.


;We’re working on adding more languages all the time.
Ons werk daaraan om voortdurend nóg tale by te voeg.


